<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV30">
<l>vāṉakamu maṇṇakamum veṟpumēḻka ṭalkaḷum</l>
<l>pōṉakañcey tālilaittu yiṉṟapuṇṭa rīkaṉē</l>
<l>tēṉakañcey taṇṇaṟumma larttuḻāynaṉ mālaiyāy</l>
<l>kūṉakampu katteṟitta koṟṟavilli yallaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O lotus[-eyed Lord] who slept on the banyan leaf, having eaten</l>
<l>The sky, the earth, the mountains, and the seven oceans!</l>
<l>O You with good garlands of cool, fragrant, tulasi</l>
<l rend="indent">with honey-containing flowers!</l>
<l>Are You not the [Lord] with the victorious arch that shot [earthen balls]</l>
<l rend="indent">In such a way that [Mantharā’s] hunchback sank in?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
